@startuml
actor Conductor
participant TicketForm
participant ITicketingService
participant IDevice
Conductor -> TicketForm: Fill passenger + select from/to
TicketForm -> TicketForm: Validate
TicketForm -> ITicketingService: CreateTicket(ticket)
ITicketingService -> IDevice: Print(ticket)
IDevice --> ITicketingService: OK
ITicketingService --> TicketForm: success
TicketForm --> Conductor: show success
@enduml